metadata.name: Wuta #01
metadata.description:
This shot was taken from a bonfire event with more detail on the fire lit as a torch.

There's so much you can do and achieve when you have fire on the inside of you. Greatness and Prominence are inevitable when that fire is on the inside, burning and never going out.

There's so much you can see when there's light from the burning fire on your inside. Keep your fire burning. Don't let it go out.
